# AgentCube Implementation Plan (AR-034 to AR-043)

## Overview

This plan maps Architectural Requirements AR-034 through AR-043 to specific files and implementation logic. These ARs represent the core session management, routing, idle cleanup, and code execution functionality.

---

## AR Mapping

| AR | Component | Description |
|----|-----------|-------------|
| AR-034 | Store Interface | Define Store interface contract |
| AR-035 | Redis Provider | Redis implementation of Store |
| AR-036 | Valkey Provider | Valkey implementation of Store |
| AR-037 | Storage Singleton | Singleton Storage() + provider selection |
| AR-038 | Session Manager | Session resolution and creation |
| AR-039 | Reverse Proxy | Proxy to sandbox with JWT injection |
| AR-040 | HTTP Server | Server with health endpoints + middleware |
| AR-041 | Idle Cleanup | Controller for idle sandbox deletion |
