### Logic Flow
1. Connect to Redis using REDIS_ADDR and REDIS_PASSWORD
2. Implement all Store interface methods
3. Use Redis transactions (TxPipelined) for atomic operations
4. Maintain two sorted sets: expiry and last_activity
5. Return ErrNotFound on missing keys
6. Handle password requirement based on REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED

